2.00	A_Prize_of_Gold	A Prize of Gold	A Prize of Gold is a British 1955 Warwick Films heist film directed by Mark Robson partly filmed in West Berlin. The film stars Richard Widmark as a United States Air Force Air Police Master Sergeant motivated by love and compassion to begin a life of crime. It was based on the 1953 novel by Max Catto.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/4/48/APrizeofGold1S.jpg/220px-APrizeofGold1S.jpg
